The paper deals with the transmission of information over a fading channel, which is a common topic in the information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM) sub-categories. The use of limited peakedness input and peak-to-average power ratio constraints suggests a focus on signal processing (cs.SI) and networking (cs.NI) aspects. The proposed signaling scheme also involves optimization, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.MA) sub-category.
